        "title": "JVM_Bind when running OSGi application from Eclipse",
        "body": "<p>I have the following problem.<\/p>\n\n<p>I have a run-configuration (osgi-type) in Eclipse. Once upon a time this run configuration ran fine, without any problems.<\/p>\n\n<p>Now when I try to run it I get a <code>java.net.BindException: Address already in use: JVM_Bind<\/code> and all the rows printed in the console are printed twice.<\/p>\n\n<p>I see that the application is started on port xxxx and then a couple of rows later I get the error.<\/p>\n\n<p>The run-configuration hasn't changed.<\/p>\n\n<p>Any ideas?<\/p>\n",
