        "creation_date": 1351004811,
        "body": "<p>The exception is due to an application trying to bind to a server port, while the port has already been taken by another application.<\/p>\n\n<p>You also mention every row in the console is printed twice. This means the application is probably launched twice.<\/p>\n\n<p>There is not enough information to determine why your run configuration launches the same application twice. You should look at the DEBUG perspective in Eclipse to see whether a single process was launched with two threads.<\/p>\n",
